Dialogue: 0.0:46:36.96.0:46:38.87.Zain..0.0.0..ayolah. McVries.\NJangan ganggu dia. kawan.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:38.93.0:46:40.00.Zain..0.0.0..Semalam dia tidak tidur nyenyak.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:40.07.0:46:41.17.Zain..0.0.0..Dia juga tidak baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:41.24.0:46:43.71.Zain..0.0.0..Hei. bagaimana tidurmu hari ini? Hah?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:43.77.0:46:45.84.Zain..0.0.0..Karena aku tidur\Nsangat nyenyak.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:45.91.0:46:47.47.Zain..0.0.0..Hei. Olson.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:47.54.0:46:48.64.Zain..0.0.0..Kau mau jalan-jalan?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:49.41.0:46:50.44.Zain..0.0.0..Pergi ke neraka.
