Dialogue: 0.0:46:52.91.0:46:55.22.Zain..0.0.0..- Apa katamu?\N- Pergi ke neraka. Kubilang...
Dialogue: 0.0:46:55.28.0:46:56.52.Zain..0.0.0..Pergi ke neraka!
Dialogue: 0.0:46:59.59.0:47:00.89.Zain..0.0.0..Hanya mencoba\Nmembuatnya menarik.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:00.95.0:47:03.39.Zain..0.0.0..- Hmm.\N- {\i1}Peringatan.{\i}
