Dialogue: 0.1:07:06.33.1:07:07.49.Zain..0.0.0..Garraty.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:10.36.1:07:11.70.Zain..0.0.0..Kau lelah. Garraty?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:13.60.1:07:15.40.Zain..0.0.0..Apa aku lelah?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:15.47.1:07:17.71.Zain..0.0.0..Ya...\NYa. aku agak lelah.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:17.77.1:07:18.97.Zain..0.0.0..Sangat lelah?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:20.34.1:07:21.48.Zain..0.0.0..Hampir.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:23.28.1:07:24.31.Zain..0.0.0..Tidak.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:25.18.1:07:26.61.Zain..0.0.0..Kau tidak sangat lelah.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:26.68.1:07:29.65.Zain..0.0.0..Belum.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:29.72.1:07:31.59.Zain..0.0.0..Entah kenapa aku bicara padamu.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:31.65.1:07:34.52.Zain..0.0.0..Seperti bicara\Npada asap.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:35.32.1:07:37.53.Zain..0.0.0..Olson sangat lelah.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:37.59.1:07:39.33.Zain..0.0.0..Dia hampir selesai.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:41.30.1:07:44.03.Zain..0.0.0..Berani sekali kau bicara soal Olson.\Ndengan kondisimu itu.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:45.50.1:07:47.17.Zain..0.0.0..Dia buang air di celana.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:47.23.1:07:48.84.Zain..0.0.0..Kau mencium baunya?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:48.90.1:07:49.94.Zain..0.0.0..Aku saja bisa.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:50.00.1:07:51.61.Zain..0.0.0..Apa maksudmu. kawan?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:51.67.1:07:54.31.Zain..0.0.0..Kenapa tidak tanya teman kampungmu.\NArt Baker?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:54.37.1:07:57.34.Zain..0.0.0..Keledai tidak suka membajak.\Ntapi dia suka wortel enak.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:57.41.1:07:58.81.Zain..0.0.0..{\i1}Peringatan ketiga. Nomor 23.{\i}
Dialogue: 0.1:07:58.88.1:08:00.72.Zain..0.0.0..Perhatikan Olson.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:00.78.1:08:04.52.Zain..0.0.0..Dia belum sadar.\Ntapi dia sudah kehilangan\Nselera pada wortel itu.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:04.59.1:08:06.19.Zain..0.0.0..{\i1}Peringatan pertama. Nomor 46.{\i}
