Dialogue: 0.1:08:11.93.1:08:13.26.Zain..0.0.0..Olson. bicara padaku.\NAda apa?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:13.33.1:08:14.43.Zain..0.0.0..Hei. hei.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:14.49.1:08:16.30.Zain..0.0.0..Bicara padaku. Hank.
