Dialogue: 0.1:08:27.51.1:08:29.58.Zain..0.0.0..Taman Tuhan.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:34.38.1:08:36.22.Zain..0.0.0..Penuh rumput liar.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:37.72.1:08:39.85.Zain..0.0.0..- Hank. Hank!\N- {\i1}Peringatan. 46.{\i}
Dialogue: 0.1:08:39.92.1:08:41.02.Zain..0.0.0..- Hei.\N- Hei. terus jalan.
